# This app does NOT read API keys from secrets — on purpose.
#
# Team Doctor is bring-your-own-key: each person pastes their own key into the
# sidebar, and it lives only in that browser session. This guarantees a visitor
# can never spend the owner's API quota.
#
# So you do NOT need a secrets.toml, and you should NOT put an API key in
# Streamlit Cloud -> App settings -> Secrets. If one is already there, delete it.
#
# (The deterministic health check — samples and the build-your-team form — needs
# no key at all.)
